---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy — Recverse"
  description="Information about how Recverse processes personal data on this website."
>
  <div class="landing-page landing-page--privacy">
    <section class="section legal-section">
      <div class="container legal-container">
        <p class="eyebrow">Legal</p>
        <h1>Privacy</h1>
        <p class="lead legal-lead">
          This notice briefly explains which personal data may be processed on this website,
          for what purpose, and who you can contact if you have questions.
        </p>

        <div class="legal-box">
          <h2>Responsible party</h2>
          <p><strong>Domenico Recchia</strong></p>
          <p>6042 Dietwil, Aargau, Switzerland</p>
          <p>
            Please use the <a href="/en/contact/">contact form</a> for inquiries.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-box">
          <h2>What data may be processed</h2>
          <p>
            If you use the contact form, the information you enter may be processed. This may include,
            in particular, your name, email address, message, and optional information such as company,
            phone number, role, budget, timeline, or topic selections.
          </p>
          <p>
            In addition, technical metadata or log data may be generated as part of normal website
            operation, such as the time of the request, IP address, browser information, or similar
            connection-related data.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-box">
          <h2>Purpose of processing</h2>
          <p>
            Processing takes place to receive and respond to inquiries, assess the matter,
            prepare a reasonable next step, and, where appropriate, initiate a conversation
            or offer.
          </p>
          <p>
            Based on the current setup, no separate tracking or analytics tools for behavioral
            analysis are being used on this website.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-box">
          <h2>Hosting and form processing</h2>
          <p>
            This website is hosted on Netlify. Forms may be processed through Netlify Forms
            so that requests can be received and routed technically.
          </p>
          <p>
            It cannot be ruled out that technical processing steps may also involve systems
            outside Switzerland. For that reason, please do not submit unnecessary sensitive
            information at first contact.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-box">
          <h2>Technical logs and spam protection</h2>
          <p>
            To operate the website securely and reduce misuse, technical logs and simple
            protections against automated submissions may be used.
          </p>
          <p>
            This may include, in particular, server-side logs, form-related metadata, and
            simple technical checks connected to the use of the contact form.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-box">
          <h2>Retention</h2>
          <p>
            Requests and related data are generally retained only as long as necessary to
            process the request, provide reasonable follow-up, and, where relevant, meet
            business or legal documentation needs.
          </p>
          <p>
            Unless longer statutory obligations apply, no unnecessary long-term storage is intended.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-box">
          <h2>Fonts and external resources</h2>
          <p>
            Based on the current setup, the fonts used on this website are served locally / self-hosted.
            This means that no additional connection to external font services is required solely for font rendering.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-box">
          <h2>Your rights</h2>
          <p>
            Subject to applicable law, you may in particular request information about the data
            processed in relation to you, as well as correction or deletion, unless legal or
            legitimate grounds prevent this.
          </p>
          <p>
            Please use the <a href="/en/contact/">contact form</a> for such requests.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-box legal-box--subtle">
          <h2>Note</h2>
          <p>
            This privacy notice may be updated if technical processes, services used, or legal
            requirements change.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>

  <style>
    .landing-page--privacy .legal-section {
      padding-top: 6.5rem;
      padding-bottom: 5rem;
    }

    .landing-page--privacy .legal-container {
      max-width: 820px;
    }

    .landing-page--privacy h1 {
      max-width: none;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .landing-page--privacy .legal-lead {
      max-width: 60ch;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .landing-page--privacy .legal-box {
      background: var(--rv-bg-soft);
      border: 1px solid var(--rv-border);
      border-radius: 18px;
      padding: 1.25rem 1.35rem;
      margin-top: 1rem;
      box-shadow: var(--rv-shadow);
      backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    }

    .landing-page--privacy .legal-box h2 {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      max-width: none;
      margin-bottom: 0.9rem;
    }

    .landing-page--privacy .legal-box p,
    .landing-page--privacy .legal-box li {
      color: var(--rv-text-soft);
      line-height: 1.75;
    }

    .landing-page--privacy .legal-box p {
      margin: 0 0 0.8rem;
    }

    .landing-page--privacy .legal-box p:last-child {
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    .landing-page--privacy .legal-box a {
      color: var(--rv-accent);
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    .landing-page--privacy .legal-box--subtle {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.025);
      box-shadow: none;
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .landing-page--privacy .legal-section {
        padding-top: 5.5rem;
      }

      .landing-page--privacy .legal-box {
        padding: 1rem 1.05rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</BaseLayout>